This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it deals with topic modeling of textual corpora. Additionally, the use of neural networks and Gaussian mixture models suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions retrieval accuracy and classification accuracy, indicating that it may be relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of word distributions and the use of embeddings suggests that it may also be relevant to Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category.
